OL,3,CPolice slam drone user for
OL,4,C'irresponsible flying' during Lake
OL,5,CDistrict rescue
OL,7,FPolice in the Lake District have
OL,8,Fslammed a drone user for
OL,9,F"irresponsible flying" during a rescue
OL,10,Fmission on Sunday afternoon.
OL,12,FSouth Lakes police were taking part in
OL,13,Fa multi-agency mountain rescue when
OL,14,Ftheir efforts were "severely hampered."
OL,16,FOfficers say the drone pilot risked
OL,17,Fthe safety of everyone taking part in
OL,18,Fthe rescue and the dignity of the
OL,19,Fcasualty.
