OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776687066
OL,3,CPolice slam drone user for
OL,4,C'irresponsible flying' during Lake
OL,5,CDistrict rescue
OL,7,FIn a statement on social media, the
OL,8,Fforce said: "South Lakes Police
OL,9,Fassisted in a multi-agency mountain
OL,10,Frescue of a seriously injured casualty
OL,11,Fthis afternoon in Langdale.
OL,13,F"The casualty was eventually airlifted
OL,14,Ffrom the side of the fell by a
OL,15,Fcoastguard helicopter. This rescue
OL,16,Feffort was severely hampered by the
OL,17,Firresponsible flying of a drone in the
OL,18,Flocality.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/3
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
