OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776687066
OL,3,CPolice slam drone user for
OL,4,C'irresponsible flying' during Lake
OL,5,CDistrict rescue
OL,7,F"The reckless actions of the drone
OL,8,Fpilot not only risked the safety of
OL,9,Fthe coastguard helicopter and crew but
OL,10,Falso the safety and dignity of the
OL,11,Fcasualty.
OL,13,F"Please ensure drones are used in a
OL,14,Fresponsible and legal manner."
